casebody.data:
Evalon S. Moses, Appellant, vs. B. F. Irvine & Co., Respondents. APPEAL PROM THE DISTRICT COURT OP RAMSEY COUNTY. It appears from the order in this cause, that it was originally a Certiorari from a judgment of a Justice of the Peace.

A motion was made in the District Court, to quash the writ ■of Certiorari, which motion was denied

The order denying the motion was reversed in the Supreme Court, but the order of reversal is the only paper which can be found on file.
